&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have 3+ years of experience in PV reliability, or failure analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are familiar with PV reliability test standards and methods&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are familiar with module and material characterization and analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are proficient in reliability tools and statistical analysis software (e.g. Jmp)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have a proven ability to work well with cross-functional teams&amp;nbsp; (R&amp;amp;D, Engineering, Manufacturing) – showing strong communication and empathy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enjoy the challenges that come with working at a startup&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
