&lt;li&gt;Experience in sourcing reliability test equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience partnering with engineering and manufacturing teams to identify issues, troubleshoot, and solve problems&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An understanding of why solving climate change is an urgent and critical challenge&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
